---

<Layout
  title="Digital rekvisita för film och TV"
  description="Interaktiv digital design och grafiska lösningar för TV och filmproduktioner. Vi skräddarsyr fiktiva gränssnitt för alla typer av skärmar och enheter."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Nav -->
    <nav id="start">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
          <img
            src="/images/68dc26a8c975bbe237511944_digitalrekvisita_logo.svg"
            alt="Digitalrekvisita"
          />
        </a>
        <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Meny" aria-expanded="false">
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
        </button>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#tjanster">Tjänster</a>
          <a href="#om">Om oss</a>
          <a href="#om">Kontakt</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="hero">
      <video
        class="hero-video"
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        poster="/images/672e02bcb1f35afa9ce8b9a1_digitalrekvisita_crop-poster-00001.jpg"
      >
        <source
          src="/videos/672e02bcb1f35afa9ce8b9a1_digitalrekvisita_crop-transcode.mp4"
          type="video/mp4"
        />
        <source
          src="/videos/672e02bcb1f35afa9ce8b9a1_digitalrekvisita_crop-transcode.webm"
          type="video/webm"
        />
      </video>
    </header>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-grid">
          <div class="intro-left">
            <h2>Vi skräddarsyr fiktiva gränssnitt för alla typer av skärmar och enheter</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-right">
            <p>
              Med fokus på <strong>interaktiv</strong> digital design levererar
              vi trovärdiga grafiska lösningar för TV och filmproduktioner. Vi
              ger er full kontroll över digitala sekvenser som ska visas i bild.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Projects -->
    <section class="projects">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="projects-grid">
          {projects.map((project) => <ProjectCard {...project} />)}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section class="services" id="tjanster">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="services-left">
            <h2>Våra tjänster</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="services-right">
            <div class="service-group">
              <div class="service-icon">
                <img
                  src="/images/63c43b67cff8186460064543_icon_digital.png"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>Digital rekvisita</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Interaktiva flöden för smartphones och datorer</li>
                  <li>Tidsbestämda utlösare (t.ex. inkommande SMS)</li>
                  <li>Fejkappar och hemsidor</li>
                  <li>Rörlig grafik</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-group">
              <div class="service-icon">
                <img
                  src="/images/63c43b5c1c217847b6c73d01_icon_grafisk.png"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>Grafisk rekvisita</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Helhetslösningar inom grafisk design</li>
                  <li>Logotyper</li>
                  <li>Skyltning och originalframställning</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-group">
              <div class="service-icon">
                <img
                  src="/images/63c43b45ee0d0f2859b941e1_icon_kreativ.png"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>Fysisk rekvisita & kreativa lösningar</h3>
                <p class="service-note">
                  Vi samarbetar med <a
                    href="https://www.toolspace.se/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener">Toolspace AB</a
                  > och har därmed också kompetens och möjligheter att tillverka
                  fysisk rekvisita!
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Tillgång till 3D-printers & 3D scanning</li>
                  <li>Verkstäder: trä, metall, textil</li>
                  <li>Laserskärare och CNC maskiner</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Logos -->
    <section class="logos" id="kunder">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="logos-grid">
          {
            logos.map((logo) => (
              <img
                src={`/images/${logo.src}`}
                alt={logo.alt}
                class="logo-img"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="about" id="om">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-left">
            <h2>Om oss</h2>
            <p>
              Vi har över 10 års erfarenhet inom grafisk design och
              interaktionsdesign. De senaste åren har vi nischat oss på
              interaktiv digital rekvisita och tagit oss an en mängd roliga
              uppdrag inom filmindustrin. Vi har alltid personlig kundkontakt,
              en förståelse för drama och ett öga för detalj. Tveka inte att
              höra av er!
            </p>
            <p class="instagram-note">
              Följ oss gärna på Instagram: <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/digitalrekvisita"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener">@digitalrekvisita</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-right">
            <div class="team-member">
              <img
                src="/images/68dc463d868ab229f5e0d63c_carl_bw_Ny.avif"
                alt="Carl Waerner"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="member-info">
                <strong>Carl Waerner</strong>
                <span>carl.waerner@gmail.com</span>
                <a href="tel:+46708276741">070-827 67 41</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
              <img
                src="/images/68dc1d5fcc32f7856dfef49b_frida_bw.avif"
                alt="Frida Häggström Gerdt"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="member-info">
                <strong>Frida Häggström Gerdt</strong>
                <span>frida.haggstrom@gmail.com</span>
                <a href="tel:+46762566882">076-256 68 82</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <img
          src="/images/68dc26a8c975bbe237511944_digitalrekvisita_logo.svg"
          alt="Digitalrekvisita"
          class="footer-logo"
        />
        <a href="#start" class="to-top">Till toppen</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Container */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Nav */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  nav.scrolled {
    background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .nav-logo img {
    height: 24px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: #05ff00;
  }

  .nav-toggle {
    display: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .nav-toggle span {
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #fff;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 500px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* Intro */
  .intro {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .intro-left h2 {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .intro-right p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro-right strong {
    color: #05ff00;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Projects */
  .projects {
    padding: 0 0 4rem;
  }

  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  /* Services */
  .services {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .services-left h2 {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .services-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .service-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .service-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .service-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .service-group h3 {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-group ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .service-group li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .service-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-note a {
    color: #05ff00;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Logos */
  .logos {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .logos-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2.5rem 3rem;
  }

  .logo-img {
    height: 40px;
    width: auto;
    opacity: 0.7;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .logo-img:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .about-left h2 {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-left p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .instagram-note a {
    color: #05ff00;
  }

  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .team-member {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .team-member img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .member-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .member-info strong {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .member-info span,
  .member-info a {
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .member-info a:hover {
    color: #05ff00;
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .to-top {
    font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .to-top:hover {
    color: #05ff00;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.98);
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      z-index: 99;
    }

    .nav-links.open {
      display: flex;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav-toggle {
      display: flex;
      z-index: 101;
    }

    .nav-toggle.open span:nth-child(1) {
      transform: rotate(45deg) translate(5px, 5px);
    }

    .nav-toggle.open span:nth-child(2) {
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .nav-toggle.open span:nth-child(3) {
      transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(5px, -5px);
    }

    .intro-grid,
    .services-grid,
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-left h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero {
      height: 60vh;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Nav scroll effect
  const nav = document.querySelector("nav");
  window.addEventListener("scroll", () => {
    if (window.scrollY > 50) {
      nav?.classList.add("scrolled");
    } else {
      nav?.classList.remove("scrolled");
    }
  });

  // Mobile menu toggle
  const toggle = document.querySelector(".nav-toggle");
  const links = document.querySelector(".nav-links");
  toggle?.addEventListener("click", () => {
    toggle.classList.toggle("open");
    toggle.setAttribute(
      "aria-expanded",
      toggle.classList.contains("open").toString()
    );
    links?.classList.toggle("open");
  });

  // Close menu on link click
  links?.querySelectorAll("a").forEach((a) => {
    a.addEventListener("click", () => {
      toggle?.classList.remove("open");
      links?.classList.remove("open");
    });
  });
</script>
